2. Install DX8.1<br>
<br>
About Testing: It is impossible to test for even 1% of the possible system configs.<br>
<br>
How many different proccessors are there? How many vid cards 100? How many different RAM configs? how many different sound cards? how many different modems? how many driver versions for all of the above? how many different OS versions? <br>
It is alot easier to find bugs when you have 200,000 people playing on an esentialy unique platform then with even a  &quot;massive&quot; 1000 person/computer QA department.<br>
